OOC:Tell me what ya think about this char introduction

:::Sky Lynx:::

::The great shuttle had been flying through space for some time now.  he had 
left Cybertron long ago when he was unaccepted by the Maximals.  Why are all 
these veterans shunned? His Shuttle mode was as big as ever, but his bird and 
lynx forms were considerably smaller now.  He went to a place he hadnt flown 
to in centuries.  It was a place known as earth.  He wondered what was going 
on there now::
Computer: Warning, this zone is off limits by the high council
Sky Lynx: Slag the high council!
::He flies down to the planet and learns that he is in past earth, and that 
there is a great war going on::
Sky Lynx: Well, i must offer my services.
::He goes to the CF and opens a comm::
Sky Lynx: I would like to join you maximals.  Do you accept?
